      "id": "jep530-baseline",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "NotebookUtils.banner(\"Non-preview baseline: manual handling of primitives\");\nObject any = java.util.concurrent.ThreadLocalRandom.current().nextBoolean() ? 42 : 3.14159;\nif (any instanceof Integer i) { // pattern for reference types (already GA)\n    NotebookUtils.kv(\"kind\", \"Integer\");\n    NotebookUtils.kv(\"value\", i);\n} else if (any instanceof Double d) {\n    NotebookUtils.kv(\"kind\", \"Double\");\n    NotebookUtils.kv(\"value\", d);\n} else {\n    NotebookUtils.kv(\"kind\", any.getClass().getName());\n    NotebookUtils.kv(\"value\", any);\n}\nNotebookUtils.hr();\nIO.println(\"Preview (JEP 530) extends patterns to primitive types and allows use in instanceof/switch.\");",
      "metadata": {
